entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Syirlabradawk has been rescued from the forces of the N.S.H. and has made his way to safety.
entries.journal_entry_description: Trezya Nenei has asked that her friend, Syirlabradawk, a medical officer recently captured by the N.S.H., be rescued.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Trezya has a good friend, a wookiee medical officer named Syirlabradawk, who has been captured by the Nightstrike Soldier Hegemony.  He will soon be transferred to Imperial custody and likely enslaved or executed.  Trezya desperately want him to be rescued. Find an N.S.H. mainframe access terminal and slice it to find where they are holding the wookiee.
entries.task01_message_box_text: The N.S.H. network is slow and moments tick by as the slicing routines run their course.  Finally the location of Syirlabradawk, the Wookiee medical officer Trezya is looking for, spools onto the screen.  He is being held on this level in the dention block.  After a few more tedious moments slicing through N.S.H.'s incredibly slow network, the security screens in the cells have come down, though there are still guards stationed there.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The N.S.H. mainframe indicated that Syirlabradawk was being held in the prison pens on the primary level of the base.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find Syirlabradawks medical tools so he can treat his fellow prisoners before he escapes.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Syirlabradawk with the tools.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: A supply officer in the base has Syir's chemicals bag.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Syir suggested finding an EmDee droid in the base as they usually carry surgical tools on them.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Syir said that an officer in the torture chamber has his bio analyzer.
